1
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:11,460
♪Just To Meet You, you fell for me♪

2
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:15,460
♪Just to meet me, into my trap you fell♪

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:19,240
♪Wanna try a breathless love?♪

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:23,490
♪Every move hits the heart, close and sure♪

5
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:27,460
♪Just To Meet You, you love my playful charm♪

6
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,480
♪Just to meet me,
my romantic little schemes for you♪

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:35,170
♪Wanna play another brand-new game?♪

8
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:39,940
♪Layer by layer, we close the gap♪

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:46,820
=Just To Meet You=

10
00:00:46,820 --> 00:00:48,740
=Episode 15=
=Liu Yexi dies, Ye Lang suspected=

11
00:01:00,070 --> 00:01:01,390
What do I have to do

12
00:01:02,430 --> 00:01:03,640
for you to believe me?

13
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:11,120
I brought this on myself.

14
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:13,230
It's all my fault.

15
00:01:17,040 --> 00:01:17,880
Niannian.

16
00:01:18,230 --> 00:01:19,520
Niannian. It's you.

17
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:26,840
- Wanna run?
- Let go!

18
00:01:27,710 --> 00:01:29,310
You faked being unstable this long,

19
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:31,230
and now you can't keep it up?

20
00:01:32,220 --> 00:01:33,710
I've wanted out of this home for long.

21
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:35,760
This place is a grave!

22
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,790
Everyone here is fake.

23
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:38,960
It's disgusting!

24
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:40,390
And you,

25
00:01:40,510 --> 00:01:41,480
you brat!

26
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:43,280
Why didn't you

27
00:01:43,300 --> 00:01:44,950
die with your mother?

28
00:01:45,180 --> 00:01:46,420
What's the point of you living?

29
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:51,200
You're the last one
who gets to say that!

30
00:01:55,310 --> 00:01:56,230
I won't kill you.

31
00:01:57,510 --> 00:01:59,150
Trash like you

32
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:02,040
should rot in the Li family.

33
00:02:11,870 --> 00:02:12,710
Let go of me!

34
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:13,800
Let go!

35
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:17,430
Ye Lang.

36
00:02:17,630 --> 00:02:19,630
Do you know why Jiang Niannian left?

37
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:23,280
She saw through the Li family.

38
00:02:23,630 --> 00:02:24,800
She thinks you're filthy.

39
00:02:25,630 --> 00:02:26,470
Because you

40
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:28,400
and me,
and your father are all the same!

41
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:30,280
So fake!

42
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:31,590
So disgusting!

43
00:02:34,230 --> 00:02:35,080
It's actually

44
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:37,840
all filthy tricks.

45
00:02:39,190 --> 00:02:40,190
This place

46
00:02:40,750 --> 00:02:42,430
is nothing but a grave!

47
00:02:42,590 --> 00:02:43,520
Liu Yexi.

48
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,030
You've planned this for years

49
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:46,120
and schemed every step,

50
00:02:46,190 --> 00:02:48,470
just so your son gets the Li family,
isn't it?

51
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,190
Other than poison,

52
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:55,000
what other dirty tricks do you have?

53
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,190
Use them all.

54
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:59,190
I'm waiting for you to end me.

55
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,360
Ye Lang.

56
00:03:01,710 --> 00:03:03,000
You're the real madman!

57
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:27,960
Ma'am.

58
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,520
Ma'am took her own life!

59
00:03:39,590 --> 00:03:41,430
I don't believe Mom would do that.

60
00:03:42,750 --> 00:03:44,360
She hasn't even seen me get married.

61
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:47,630
Make arrangements ASAP.

62
00:03:48,910 --> 00:03:49,840
Tell the public

63
00:03:50,630 --> 00:03:52,280
it was a sudden illness.

64
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,240
Dad.

65
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,360
Master.

66
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,680
Last night,

67
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,120
I witnessed

68
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,360
Young Master and Ma'am

69
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,680
had a clash in the foyer.

70
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:04,960
Young Master even

71
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,150
grabbed Ma'am by the throat.

72
00:04:09,630 --> 00:04:10,470
You...

73
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,400
saw it wrong.

74
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,750
There are indeed

75
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:18,000
finger marks on her neck.

76
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,720
Just like Liu said.

77
00:04:21,310 --> 00:04:22,150
You...

78
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,520
Why?

79
00:04:23,830 --> 00:04:25,040
She did hurt you before.

80
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,120
But why did you get her killed?

81
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,320
Mr. Li.

82
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:29,600
If this gets out of hand,

83
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,120
it becomes a criminal case.

84
00:04:31,630 --> 00:04:33,750
Young Master may
have to go to the police station.

85
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:35,020
Ye Lang isn't going anywhere.

86
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,190
I've never seen a case

87
00:04:52,190 --> 00:04:53,560
where one gets sent to the police

88
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,600
before the facts are even clear.

89
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,200
Niannian.

90
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:05,800
The priority is

91
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,800
to send the body

92
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,240
for an autopsy

93
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:11,600
not to send an innocent man in.

94
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,630
Ms. Jiang, you've misunderstood.

95
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,600
Young Master just needs

96
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,000
to give a voluntary statement.

97
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,000
If the police find out first

98
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,000
and come arrest him,

99
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:20,960
that would be worse.

100
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:23,600
We might need a lot for bail then.

101
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:26,000
If there's bail to be paid,

102
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,390
you won't need to cover it.

103
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:30,880
He is my husband.

104
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,080
I'll pay it.

105
00:05:32,230 --> 00:05:34,930
♪I'm going nowhere♪

106
00:05:34,950 --> 00:05:37,080
How much does she owe you?
I'll pay it.

107
00:05:45,190 --> 00:05:46,030
Niannian.

108
00:05:46,310 --> 00:05:47,150
You're back.

109
00:05:51,070 --> 00:05:51,910
Niannian.

110
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,440
Don't get it wrong.

111
00:05:56,830 --> 00:05:57,800
I just saw the news,

112
00:05:58,750 --> 00:06:00,320
and you helped me before.

113
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:01,960
We're even now.

114
00:06:05,190 --> 00:06:07,430
You gave me this card before.

115
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:08,840
I'm giving it back.

116
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:15,640
So,

117
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:19,480
you didn't forgive me...

118
00:06:20,870 --> 00:06:22,000
I don't like

119
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:24,070
owing anyone anything.

120
00:06:24,310 --> 00:06:25,720
(She's willing to spend on me,)

121
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:27,360
(it means she still cares.)

122
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:29,480
(Even if she only loves my money.)

123
00:06:29,870 --> 00:06:30,950
(Loving my money)

124
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:31,940
(is loving me, isn't it?)

125
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,200
By the way,

126
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,750
I found this in Zhong Minghui's

127
00:06:35,750 --> 00:06:36,590
secret email.

128
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:39,120
It should help you.

129
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,120
Could it be

130
00:06:46,830 --> 00:06:47,950
Li Hong is actually

131
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:51,560
the son of Liu Yexi and Zhong Minghui?

132
00:06:53,870 --> 00:06:55,160
Do his age match?

133
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,080
Besides,

134
00:06:57,260 --> 00:06:58,240
we can't say it's Li Hong

135
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,830
from just one photo.

136
00:07:01,190 --> 00:07:02,430
We need stronger proof.

137
00:07:06,270 --> 00:07:07,190
A DNA test.

138
00:07:12,830 --> 00:07:13,670
You're here.

139
00:07:14,630 --> 00:07:15,830
I'd like to talk to you.

140
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,270
You want to ask

141
00:07:19,270 --> 00:07:21,510
why I refused to look into Liu Yexi's death,

142
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:23,440
right?

143
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,240
She's dead.

144
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:27,840
It's over.

145
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,560
Everything ends there.

146
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,950
When my mother died,

147
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:35,680
you were the same way.

148
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,360
Like their deaths

149
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:40,160
meant nothing to you.

150
00:07:42,510 --> 00:07:43,680
You're good at everything

151
00:07:45,270 --> 00:07:46,800
except dealing with people.

152
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,430
You let emotions get in the way.

153
00:07:49,070 --> 00:07:50,390
Just like your mother.

154
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,040
That's the one thing

155
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,560
that makes me hesitate

156
00:07:56,190 --> 00:07:57,680
to hand our family over to you.

157
00:07:58,390 --> 00:07:59,720
I just don't understand

158
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:04,680
why you're always so cold.

159
00:08:05,830 --> 00:08:07,160
When my mother passed away,

160
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,870
you didn't shed a single tear.

161
00:08:09,430 --> 00:08:10,430
Now Liu Yexi is dead,

162
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,750
and you're still the same!

163
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:17,190
Family interests always come first.

164
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,120
One day,

165
00:08:29,070 --> 00:08:30,630
when you take over the Li family,

166
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,360
you'll understand.

167
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:34,320
I'm doing this

168
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,670
for your good.

169
00:09:01,870 --> 00:09:03,080
You got her killed.

170
00:09:04,390 --> 00:09:05,750
Are you ready to pay for it?

171
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,840
Do you love her that much?

172
00:09:15,390 --> 00:09:17,720
This is the paternity test
for Li Hong and Li Zhongtian.

173
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:22,000
You're just some outsider's child.

174
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,360
Don't try framing Master Li Hong.

175
00:09:26,670 --> 00:09:27,580
Do you dare look at it?

176
00:09:40,550 --> 00:09:41,440
So you all knew.

177
00:09:44,030 --> 00:09:45,440
I never meant to betray Master.

178
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,840
But Ma'am was so pitiful back then.

179
00:09:51,390 --> 00:09:52,510
I wasn't even twenty.

180
00:09:53,790 --> 00:09:55,150
I gave in to temptation.

181
00:09:56,310 --> 00:09:57,150
Hong doesn't know.

182
00:09:57,150 --> 00:09:58,390
He has nothing to do with it.

183
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,200
Please don't tell him.

184
00:10:00,510 --> 00:10:01,390
He is innocent.

185
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,670
You think it's all your fault, right?

186
00:10:04,510 --> 00:10:05,350
What do you mean?

187
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:13,080
Those decades of so-called family bonds

188
00:10:14,030 --> 00:10:16,390
were all Liu Yexi's calculation.

189
00:10:16,540 --> 00:10:18,340
(Test Results)

190
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:19,740
(Biological Paternity Confirmed)

191
00:10:24,380 --> 00:10:26,150
(Biological Paternity Confirmed)
(Not mine?)

192
00:10:42,750 --> 00:10:43,590
Ever since

193
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:45,910
she told me she was pregnant,

194
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:49,360
I haven't had one good night's sleep.

195
00:10:51,510 --> 00:10:52,910
I hated myself.

196
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:54,240
I regretted everything!

197
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,040
I swore

198
00:10:56,550 --> 00:10:58,080
I would give Ma'am and my child

199
00:10:58,390 --> 00:10:59,390
the best life possible.

200
00:10:59,390 --> 00:11:00,630
I'd give everything!

201
00:11:05,150 --> 00:11:06,200
That vile woman!

202
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,080
Young Master.

203
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:10,120
Thank you for telling me the truth.

204
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,120
In return,

205
00:11:12,670 --> 00:11:13,750
I'll tell you one thing.

206
00:11:14,270 --> 00:11:15,480
Do you know how Ye Mei died?

207
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:18,630
Liu Yexi

208
00:11:18,630 --> 00:11:20,200
had me poison her medicine!

209
00:11:20,850 --> 00:11:21,720
I regret

210
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:23,030
not poisoning you too!

211
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:25,150
You should never have lived this long!

212
00:11:33,910 --> 00:11:34,750
Liu Yexi.

213
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:40,870
Liu Yexi.

214
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:44,080
Liu Yexi, you vile woman.

215
00:11:44,550 --> 00:11:46,080
You lied to me all these years!

216
00:11:47,510 --> 00:11:49,750
I won't let you have it easy in hell!

217
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:50,680
Stop him!

218
00:12:19,790 --> 00:12:26,380
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

219
00:12:28,190 --> 00:12:34,400
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

220
00:12:34,950 --> 00:12:41,950
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

221
00:12:42,700 --> 00:12:45,170
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

222
00:12:45,170 --> 00:12:50,170
♪Just for a moment to recognize you again♪

223
00:12:50,170 --> 00:12:54,400
♪You are the blazing light in my despair♪

224
00:12:54,910 --> 00:12:58,840
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

225
00:12:58,890 --> 00:13:02,680
♪I burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fire♪

226
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:08,430
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

227
00:13:08,430 --> 00:13:12,750
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

228
00:13:12,790 --> 00:13:16,610
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

229
00:13:16,620 --> 00:13:21,110
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

230
00:13:21,140 --> 00:13:25,970
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

231
00:13:26,370 --> 00:13:32,910
♪Life finds its way again♪
